data.description: Stop dreaming and start living your best Florida lifestyle! Welcome home to this waterfront tropical paradise, 4 BR/5BA custom open floor plan Pool Home, located in the prestigious gated Grand Haven, the luxurious Golf Club community known for its 18 hole Jack Nicklaus signature designed golf course. Breathtaking entryway with cathedral ceilings that leads you to the formal dining room. Separate office, warm and inviting Family room with French doors, Gourmet kitchen with white cabinets, granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, large breakfast nook overlooking at the pool and the lake. This home is an entertainment delight! Enjoy this backyard oasis, as you gather your family and friends, in your covered patio, completed with a massive screened-in oversized (36'x18') Pool and Jacuzzi with the breathtaking water views. Have your morning coffee watching the sunrise, and taking a morning splash. After a busy day have a glass of wine while enjoying your outdoor jacuzzi. A very desirable and generous size First Floor Master Bedroom with pool to water lake views. Custom made walk-in closet, a master bath that features a garden tub, his/hers vanities, and a stand alone shower. Following a luxurious stairway to the second floor, it leads to a bright and enormous Loft/Play room, adjacent to three large bedrooms, and an incredible covered balcony facing the lake. This is a fantastic Spanish Style Home in Grand Haven. This Home has Tile through out the 1st floor including all bathrooms on second floor. Open Deck and Large Solar Heated Pool for your family and friends to have fun all year long! Full pool bathroom located in the patio as well. Upstairs, guests will enjoy a large balcony with the most magnificent water views of the lake while witnessing the sunrise, the fish and turtles, while listening the birds singing. A true haven for nature lovers! Grand Haven is Live-Guard Gated Community, that offers, the 18 hole Jack Nickolas golf course, two luxurious clubhouses, with restaurant, two pools, gym, famous croquet and pickle ball courts, tennis, Zumba classes and so much more. Take a stroll along the Intracoastal paradise and enjoy what Palm Coast has to offer. Start living your best Florida lifestyle!
